{"type": "article", "id": 14050, "title": "维氏小刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-27T07:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000305HWC3jvluzUqds2gM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本文具品牌 Traveler’s Factory 联合瑞士军刀品牌 Victorinox  推出了一款限量小刀 VICTORINOX TOMO 。它采用了维氏刀具最实用的配置，包括剪刀、指甲刀、信封刀三款刀具，却仅有 6 厘米的长度，方正小巧，非常方便携带。刀具的白色外壳上印着黑色的图案和Traveler’s Factory的名言：FOR ALL THE TRAVELERS WHO HAVE A FREE SPIRIT！在强调该品牌质朴的旅行精神之外也透露出特有的文艺气。<a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/2015/08/23/victorinox-x-travelers-factory/?utm_source=feedly&amp;utm_medium=rss\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看相关信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141652Y5nkrBCVjaQIZqGv.jpg\" width=\"569\" height=\"380\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.66783831\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141653S9EmuwHUjV3gxXhF.jpg\" width=\"569\" height=\"380\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.66783831\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141654pHDWwQKx7euUTfNs.jpg\" width=\"569\" height=\"380\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.66783831\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}